<p>Hello {{ account.name }},</p>

<p><strong>Cruise Control Impact Report - {{ start_date | date: "%m/%d" }} - {{ end_date | date: "%m/%d" }}</strong></p>

<p>Here’s a snapshot of your dealership’s performance for the month:</p>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
  <tr>
    <td><strong>New conversations:</strong> {{ new_conversations }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Total messages:</strong> {{ total_messages }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>New CRM leads pushed:</strong> {{ booking_forms_completed }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>New handoff requests:</strong> {{ handoff_forms_completed }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><strong>Bookings conversion rate:</strong> {{ conversion_rate }}%</td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td style="height: 12px;"></td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
    <td>
      <strong>Bookings Estimated value: ${{ estimated_value }}</strong>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

{% if weekly_impact_chart %}
  <p><strong>Monthly performance chart</strong></p>

  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td
        style="
          padding: 12px;
          border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
          border-radius: 4px;
          background-color: #f9fafb;
          text-align: center;
        "
      >
        <img
          src="cid:{{ weekly_impact_chart_cid }}"
          alt="Weekly performance chart"
          width="420"
          style="display:block;margin:0 auto;max-width:100%;height:auto;"
        />

      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
{% endif %}

<p>Check out our <a href="https://courier.getcruisecontrol.com/hc/cruise-control-guides/articles/1766120317-weekly-impact-report-metrics-guide" style="color: #1f93ff; text-decoration: underline;">Impact reports guide</a> to understand what each of our metrics mean.</p>

<p>Visit our reports dashboard for a more detailed breakdown:</p>

<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-top: 10px;">
  <tr>
    <td>
      <a href="{{ report_url }}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 16px; background-color: #1f93ff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
        Reports Dashboard
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Cruise Control Team</p>
